      "content": "\"unauthorized access incident\" still sounds kind of scary though. people are gonna ask why it happened if we can just fix it in minutes. if we say it was a \"misconfiguration,\" it makes us look sloppy. can we just say it was part of a scheduled security audit or something? just a minor data discrepancy during a system update? i just want to avoid the word \"incident\" entirely if possible.",
